It is not convenient to apply the above procedure directly to the observed values of the variables because they have exponential growth. Thus, as the magnitude of the involved variables are very different at each time, it is difficult to apply the method. To avoid this problem, we apply the method on the following ratios: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
